OL,3,CWelsh Government hopes smoking law
OL,4,Cwill be 'strengthened'
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government says it is hoping
OL,7,Ffor a stronger approach to tackling
OL,8,Fsmoking when plans for new UK
OL,9,Fgovernment legislation are
OL,10,Freintroduced to Parliament this autumn.
OL,12,FIt follows Sir Keir Starmer's recent
OL,13,Fcomments regarding the Labour
OL,14,Fgovernment's commitment to tackle
OL,15,Fsmoking by taking further the
OL,16,Flegislation previously introduced
OL,17,Funder the Conservative party.
