OL,3,CWelsh Government hopes smoking law
OL,4,Cwill be 'strengthened'
OL,6,FReports have suggested that among
OL,7,Fthose plans is a bid to ban smoking in
OL,8,Fpub gardens and outdoor restaurants as
OL,9,Fa way to reduce the number of
OL,10,Fpreventable deaths linked to tobacco
OL,11,Fsmoke.
OL,13,FAlthough smoking bans are devolved as
OL,14,Fa health issue, the Welsh government
OL,15,Fhad already voiced its support for
OL,16,Fprevious plans for the Tobacco and
OL,17,FVapes Bill under the previous
OL,18,FConservative administration.
