OL,3,CWelsh Government hopes smoking law
OL,4,Cwill be 'strengthened'
OL,6,FThe Bill included legislation such as
OL,7,Foutlawing the sale of tobacco to
OL,8,Fanyone born in or after January 2009.
OL,10,FThe Welsh government is no stranger to
OL,11,Fsmoking restrictions in outdoor areas.
OL,12,FThey previously banned lighting up on
OL,13,Fhospitals grounds, in playgrounds or
OL,14,Fon school sites.
OL,16,FOther restrictions such as a ban on
OL,17,Fsmoking in enclosed public spaces, as
OL,18,Fwell as smoking in cars with children,
OL,19,Fhave been longstanding laws in the
OL,20,Feffort to curb the habit.
