OL,6,F"So, yes, we are going to take
OL,7,Fdecisions in this space. More details
OL,8,Fwill be revealed but this is a
OL,9,Fpreventable series of deaths and we've
OL,10,Fgot to take action to reduce the
OL,11,Fburden on the NHS and the taxpayer."
OL,13,FA Welsh government spokesperson said:
OL,14,F"We have already taken action to
OL,15,Frestrict smoking in some outdoor
OL,16,Fpublic spaces in Wales and we
OL,17,Fsupported the original UK Government
OL,18,FTobacco and Vapes Bill when it was
OL,19,Flaid in Parliament earlier this year.
