OL,3,CWelsh Government hopes smoking law
OL,4,Cwill be 'strengthened'
OL,6,F"We are committed to preventing ill
OL,7,Fhealth and supporting people to make
OL,8,Fhealthier choices for their health and
OL,9,Fwellbeing ` I therefore want us to be
OL,10,Fambitious and to take all the actions
OL,11,Fwe can to address the harms caused by
OL,12,Ftobacco.
OL,14,F"A smoke-free Wales is possible, but
OL,15,Fwe must work together for the benefits
OL,16,Fof both current and future
OL,17,Fgenerations."
OL,19,FThe alleged proposals from the UK
OL,20,Fgovernment have been met with
OL,21,Fcriticism from the hospitality sector.
